Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jubayr ibn Mut\u2019im reported: A woman came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he ordered her to return another time. She said, \u201cWhat if I come and I do not find you?\u201d It was as if she wanted to say, \"What if I find you dead?\"\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/19\/bilal-from-slave-to-master\/","url_meta":{"origin":6104,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: Bilal, from our slave to our master","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, used to say, \u201cAbu Bakr is our master and he emancipated our master,\u201d meaning Bilal. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3754 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u062c\u0627\u0628\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f\u00a0\u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648 \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0633\u064e\u064a\u0650\u0651\u062f\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0642\u064e \u0633\u064e\u064a\u0650\u0651\u062f\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0646\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6719,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/20\/abu-bakr-khalifah-imam-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":6104,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Khilafah: The Prophet orders Abu Bakr to lead prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, became ill, and when his condition was critical, he said, \u201cTell Abu Bakr to lead the people in prayer.\u201d Aisha said, \u201cHe is a soft-hearted man. He will not be able to lead in your place.\u201d The Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34420,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/09\/30\/uhud-trembles-khulafa\/","url_meta":{"origin":6104,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Uhud trembles for Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was climbing Mount Uhud with Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman when it began to quake because of them. The Prophet said, \u201cBe still, Uhud! It is but a Prophet, a truthful man, and two martyrs upon you!\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41197,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/19\/umar-on-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":6104,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Abu Bakr: He was our master, the best of us","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Abu Bakr was the most beloved of us to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, as he was the best of us and our master.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 7407 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/15\/best-ummah-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":6104,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Best of Ummah are Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: In the lifetime of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while his companions were numerous, we preferred Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman, then we would remain silent. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 4626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut Imam Ahmad commented, \u201cThe best of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6104","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection"